    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars"><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span></div>
        <p class="review-text">These guys are awesome! They answer the phone consistently so there is no dreaded feeling of getting voicemail every time, and if they can't answer, they call back promptly! Great attitudes, very helpful and very patient. I recommend that you make them your first call!</p>
        <div class="review-author">
          <div class="review-avatar">CC</div>
          <div>
            <div class="review-name">Christin Chiaramonte</div>
            <div class="review-source">Google Review</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars"><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span></div>
        <p class="review-text">Mike has gone out of his way to teach me to care for our pool correctly and calls me periodically to check in. He remembers my name and treats me with respect every time. Every part of our experience has gone better than we ever imagined. These guys do things the right way.</p>
        <div class="review-author">
          <div class="review-avatar">KG</div>
          <div>
            <div class="review-name">Kandice Gines</div>
            <div class="review-source">Google Review</div>
          </div>
        </div>
